column2: SELECT    n.objID, n.distance, n.type,   p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r,   pz.z as photoz FROM Galaxy AS G   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS n   LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid=p.objid   LEFT JOIN Photoz as pz ON n.objid=pz.objid    WHERE G.objID = n.objID   HAVING dbo.fCosmoComovDist2ObjectsRADEC(#,#,#,photoz,pra,pdec,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT,DEFAULT)<#    INTO MyDB.NearbyObjEq5
